Usage: viewSnapshot [-help] -dir <string> [-name <string>] [-view <string>]

-help             # Prints out the command usage
-dir <string>     # The directory contains the snapshot for viewing
                  # (string, required)
-name <string>    # View the specified name snapshot (string, optional)
-view <string>    # Choose to view floorplan or amoeba or place snapshot
                  # (string, optional)